{
  "text": "Our pattern generator uses a neural oscillator proposed by Matsuoka [CITATION_1] (see Figure 1 ). It consists of two excited neurons that are linked reciprocally through inhibitory connections, and each neuron has a self-inhibitory effect. The i-th oscillator is formulated by two differential equations as feedback signals Figure 1 .",
